    "The six features we use have a total of 234 dimensions, and it is worth future research to discern the validity of these dimensions.",
    "• Experimentally, KFRFIF can effectively recommend keyframes in continuous action class videos.",
    "Combining KFRFIF with some action recognition tasks [53,54] can eliminate the need for manual pre-slicing of video data, resulting in a more natural and coherent approach to these tasks.",
    "Some improvements to the constructed features may be needed for shot switching class videos to work better in the future.",
    "(a) Shot-based measure Similarity features are frequent in shot-based methods, and the keyframe extraction in the following three studies relies on the computation of frame similarity."
